### Ensure Consistent Event Emission
Make sure every state-changing function emits relevant events for transparency and off-chain sync.

```solidity
// Missing Transfer event
function transfer(address to, uint256 amount) public {
    _balances[msg.sender] -= amount;
    _balances[to] += amount;
    return true;
}
```

**Invariant:** Emit standard `Transfer` or custom events as defined in the specification.
